™tre pr√©par√© et r√©ussi. </span>\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-154 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/Al-mizaane/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/1964300-mecca-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Masjid al haram\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\">\n\nImam Ahmad DIOP organise des formations pour les p√®lerins. Le contenu de ces formations est g√©n√©ralement ax√© sur:\n\n&nbsp;', 'Accueil', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'accueil', '', '', '2019-01-17 13:43:41', '2019-01-17 13:43:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Al-mizaane/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
